p: Mineral content analysis of honey showed that the concentration of potassium was 829.55±0.51 mg/kg, sodium was 256.32 ± 0.15 mg/kg, magnesium was 61.47±0.21 mg/kg, and calcium was 166.22±0.09 mg/kg. OVEO analysis showed that the pH was 5.02, density was 0.9484 g/mL, and the refractive index was 1.5153.
